# Pinned Zellij version for the CLI Agent terminal bridge.
# install.sh reads this to download the matching x86_64-unknown-linux-musl
# build; the update pipeline (Phase 5) watches this file for bumps and
# triggers a download+zellij-web.service restart on customer machines.
#
# Validated in Phase 0 spike: claude, gemini, codex, agy all render with
# native scrollback on 0.44.3. Do not bump without re-validating the spike.
#
# Port choice: zellij-web.service binds to 9097. 9091 = orchestrator,
# 9092 = asterisk audio_subprocess, 8060-8099 = user apps, 8082 = UGV
# supervisor. 9097 is free and adjacent to the orchestrator family.
0.44.3
